channel.title: Bil's Wall Art
channel.description: These are some of the more than 100 pieces I've made. If you're interested in seeing my wall art up close and personal please contact me at BilsWallArt@hotmail.com and I'll let you know when and where the next craft fair I'll be at is. Click any image below to view it full size in your browser. Thanks for visiting my site.

item.title: Welcome to Jekyll!
item.description: Bavaria ipsum dolor sit amet g’hupft wia gsprunga wolln dringma aweng oba Biazelt hogg di hera helfgod. Sog i hawadere midananda nomoi a bissal wos gehd ollaweil gor kumm geh naa jo leck mi, Xaver: Weiznglasl i hob di liab des muas ma hoid kenna.
